title: Pluralsight - Python Desktop Application Development
description: In this course, you will learn how easy it is to write desktop applications using Python and its amazing friend, Qt. Python is famous for being simple yet powerful, and the same is true for Qt; in as little as 50 lines of code, you'll be able to write a fully functioning application. Not only that, but your application will also run on all major operating systems, and it will look like it's written for that operating system!
